label: Greenhouse Gas Emissions
note:
Air Emissions Accounts record emissions by resident units of Ireland, broken down by economic activity. Economic activities include production activities by industry (NACE Rev. 2) and consumption activities by private households, where household consumption is directly responsible for air emissions. Household air emissions are broken down by purpose (heating/cooling, transport activities, other).
